Iranian Oil Minister Gholamreza Aqazadeh United Arab Emirates ( UAE ) discus oil price general market situation , Iranian official accompanying said .
He meet UAE President Sheikh Zaid bin Sultan al-Nahayan Oil Minister Mana Said al-Oteiba .
Aqazadeh arrived last night brief stopover Riyadh , met Saudi Arabia 's Oil Minister Hisham Nazir .
The official Saudi Press Agency quoted saying talk Riyadh Nazir constructive good .
Aqazadeh said Organisation Petroleum Exporting Countries ( OPEC ) member agreed holding production stable reiterated importance maintaining oil price .
OPEC member agreed December limit production 15.8 mln barrel per day first half year benchmark price 18 dlrs barrel February 1 .
Aqazadeh also visted OPEC member Gabon , Algeria Libya .
The Iranian news agency , IRNA , quoted saying leaving Tripoli OPEC everything possible make oil price permanently stable .
